    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR\nFRANCE",
      "From:\nAir France\nPublic Relations Dept.\n683 Fifth Avenue\nNew York 22, N.Y.\nFOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE\nAN AIR FRANCE CARAVELLE JET IN FLIGHT. SEATING ACCOMMODATIONS INCLUDE\n20 FIRST CLASS SEATS AND 55 IN TOURIST. AMONG DISTINGUISHING FEATURES\nOF THIS JETLINER ARE THE TWIN JET ENGINES MOUNTED FAR BACK ON THE\nFUSELAGE. THE CARAVELLE IS A MEDIUM RANGE CRAFT AND AVERAGES 475 MILES\nPER HOUR AT A CRUISING ALTITUDE OF 30,000 FEET.\n# # #\n4/12/60"
    ],
